title: [Smuggling Tunnels, Guard Post]
description: Thick wooden timbers shore the walls and ceiling up, unbothered by time.  A sturdy wooden table sits in the center of the room, its positioning providing a good view down all of the wide tunnels surrounding it.  The remains of a deck of cards are scattered over the floor, and old weaponry leans against the walls.  Nearly unseen under the table is a small notebook.
paths: Obvious exits: southeast, south, southwest, northwest
